#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "My Submissions"
msgstr "Le mie candidature"

#: blocks/submissions/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Lists the logged-in artist's pending artwork submissions for review and "
"approval. Place this on your /my-submissions/ page or in a Site Editor "
"template."
msgstr ""
"Elenca le candidature artistiche in attesa dell'artista autenticato per "
"revisione e approvazione. Inseriscilo nella tua pagina /my-submissions/ o in "
"un template di Site Editor."

